      • getPPMatrixMap

        private Map<String,Map<String,GeneralRegressionModelEvaluator.Row>> getPPMatrixMap()
        Returns:
        A map of predictor-to-parameter correlation matrices.

        A PPMatrix element may encode zero or more matrices. Regression models return a singleton map, whereas classification models may return a singleton map or a multi-valued map, which overrides the default matrix for one or more target categories.

        The default matrix is mapped to the null key.
